{"tid":2182924,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一鍵投訴蘇文隆裁判官+鄭紀航裁判官","createTime":"2020-08-31T15:17:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T14:37:03.000Z","uid":364713,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a1c6e3b24e99be8c45989735f6845d3d1f0728c8","tid":2182924,"uid":364713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T15:17:09.000Z","msg":"(首先同大家回一回帶，大概一個月前投訴蘇文隆同香淑嫻既信喺度<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2136557/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2136557/page/1</a>)<br />\n<br />\n唔夠一個月又要寫信投訴蘇文隆，佢判咗一個廚師入獄9個月，話佢藏有瑞士條木棍係用嚟扑物件，藏有六角匙就係拎去拆鐵欄堵路<br />\n控方完全無實質證據舉證依啲觀點，蘇官再次判案完全靠估﹗﹗﹗<br />\n<br />\n鄭紀航判咗一個藏有48條6吋長(15.24cm)索帶既爸爸入獄5個半月，話佢會用索帶快速束長嚟捆綁路障堵路，但當日案發一帶並無人咁做，嗰名爸爸身上亦無其他堵路用既用具。鄭官仲唔俾嗰位爸爸保釋等上訴，佢無得見證判刑後一日佢仔仔既生日﹗大佬呀，15.24cm可以做得啲乜呀？我條賓周都唔只15.24cm啦﹗要綁啦都用繩啦，點會用索帶仲要專登駁長呀？<br />\n<br />\n所有投訴法官既文件必須郵寄，勞煩大家(1) 喺template既灰色地方輸入個人資料，(2) 印出嚟再簽名，(3) 然後郵寄。可以兩封投訴信放同一個信封。<br />\n向不公說不﹗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docdro.id/O9NiOYd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocdro.id%2FO9NiOYd&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr083u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=49ec7a4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docdro.id/O9NiOYd</a> 投訴鄭紀航信件<br />\n<a href=\"https://docdro.id/qXr7Ufl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocdro.id%2FqXr7Ufl&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr083u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=95a3984c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docdro.id/qXr7Ufl</a> 投訴蘇文隆信件"},{"pid":"3e52d476dfa29ac9569f5b77750208e353516d16","tid":2182924,"uid":321059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T15:23:01.000Z","msg":"竟然無人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f57750146879dcceb0ca314a8e7c5bf599fabfc3","tid":2182924,"uid":364713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e52d476dfa29ac9569f5b77750208e353516d16","tid":2